{"tid":1812023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克與台灣關係提升　北京或取消原定向捷克購客機計劃","createTime":"2020-01-05T08:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T08:22:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc91ff0414a527f1feff2eab2361929c046c60a3","tid":1812023,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1501080_1_L_20200105104839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1501080_1_L_20200105104839.jpg&h=09cd5e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捷克傳媒報道，北京原定計劃向捷克購買30架L-410雙引擎短程客機，但鑑於捷克與台灣關係提升，北京可能取消原本的買飛機計畫。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，總統齊曼與眾議院議長，去年4月和11月訪問北京時，曾試圖說服中方，盡快完成客機的認證，以促成交易，不過中方至今未同意。捷克總統府表示，北京因為布拉格市長賀吉普訪台，而中斷相關交易，並非不可能的事。<br />\n<br />\n捷克近年與北京的關係變得緊張，賀吉普去年10月解除布拉格與北京的姊妹市關係，並準備在本月13日與台北，締結為姊妹市，北京取消布拉格樂團在內地的巡迴演出，並中止深圳與布拉格的直航規劃。"},{"pid":"9a0fcdc8c3bfb29d7079051e6994f3cadd12d54d","tid":1812023,"uid":211941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"中華民國同捷克重新建交🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}